1. Add to the path variable the binaries
  E:\OpenCV\opencv\build\x64\vc14\bin
  
2. Solution Explorer -> Properties -> C/C++ -> Add Include directories
  E:\OpenCV\opencv\build\include
  
3. Linker -> General -> additional library directories
  E:\OpenCV\opencv\build\x64\vc14\lib;

4. Linker -> Input -> Additional Dependencies -> Copy Libraries
  opencv_world__d.lib (debug) 



After building using CMake

1. Add to the path variable the binaries
  E:\OpenCV_CUDA_GL_VS15\build\install\x64\vc14\bin
  
  E:\OpenCV_CUDA_GL_VS15\build\install\include


Setup a Cuda Runtime then follow these steps.


Configuration Properties -> CUDA C/C++ -> Additional Include Directories

C:\OpenCV_331_CUDA_GL\opencv-3.3.1\build\install\include

